{"tid":134372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個細個遇到最危險嘅事","createTime":"2017-02-25T12:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T14:27:34.000Z","uid":74002,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a18bebabe2530dedcd53e7c372d9b3c1bfbe37c","tid":134372,"uid":74002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:05:24.000Z","msg":"我先，細細個同人挽bb彈槍，攞起支槍抬番起頭時，條友响我雙眼中間射埋尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cef7c3cb82edcf45cb3b4445481db159d1add7","tid":134372,"uid":74002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:05:46.000Z","msg":"下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09438c6ca3d5e0a551d10f86f0b9fbaabe6901f6","tid":134372,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:07:53.000Z","msg":"遇到我家姐"},{"pid":"890fc432b830e9bc5ecdee6cf98cf8f4cd5478ae","tid":134372,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:08:08.000Z","msg":"你老母有危險<br />\n挽你老母"},{"pid":"dbc5cfbf1389c258e9d3fb1e38707b8f13b18af5","tid":134372,"uid":67595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:08:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我先，細細個同人挽bb彈槍，攞起支槍抬番起頭時，條友响我雙眼中間射埋尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsame 射中鼻樑位"},{"pid":"84d9b2051ea6b9b8787dcc66598c38641dcc707b","tid":134372,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老母有危險<br />\n挽你老母</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fd8d785a7de64a1ffc85b0bd360f37dde1e4f968","tid":134372,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:09:53.000Z","msg":"911果陣我就係棟野上面 果陣6歲 但呢家仲記得"},{"pid":"26da7aee736add82c364bc9b46f66e0f69df4aa1","tid":134372,"uid":63697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"係泳池遇溺3次 都係俾人救起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有一個唔知算唔算細個 應該中二左右<br />\n我成日去某個親戚屋企<br />\n由我中學開始 就有個男仔成日搭訕<br />\n應該係南亞人 但唔係中東印度 係賓秦越果啲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我初時禮貌性回覆 後尾嫌煩/驚 無視佢 之後佢冇搭過訕<br />\n但有一次放學 我架lift要等好耐 就打算搭另一部 行層樓梯落屋企<br />\n佢跟埋黎 同我去到同一個樓層<br />\n但其實佢自己住好矮 我住好高 點都唔會同一樓出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開門我打算等佢出先 佢轉左 我轉右<br />\n點知佢轉左之後又轉右跟住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我入到樓梯立刻爆發出生存本能跑到屋企門口大叫開門啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁有人開門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過咗10秒左右佢係樓梯到出黎 但路過我 去返大堂等lift<br />\n佢應該有跟住我跑 因為我明明跑得好快 但距離好似冇拉開到<br />\n從此以後冇再行過樓梯<br />\n佢之後都有跟過我幾次<br />\n下次再跟我真係踢佢幾腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb543cbe6afbfb1da013e937c4e5470a2c3512d3","tid":134372,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:52:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f6182a1166f1fc1b4b5f8e4dd4a1136c9b6a719","tid":134372,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:54:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"177fc46030feed36a2cc864702aaeb0b7ae8bc85","tid":134372,"uid":9780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:59:27.000Z","msg":"細個趕時間諗住衝紅燈，但係我果陣又細粒同埋岩岩好左邊有架巴士擋住我視線，我打算一衝果下好彩有個呀叔捉住我拉我去後，唔係嘅話2秒後我就比架巴士車埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果下嚇撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830a11500acc1debc38ebbf742caa76657b3b624","tid":134372,"uid":11161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"跌落海暈左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解要救我"},{"pid":"6018ba1da82f551a79b28ed4ee0aa97b4de9b7dd","tid":134372,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T13:06:44.000Z","msg":"係老母個肚個時，老豆想落左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4cb3b08fa2e933596e1c7915ab5b1c73661704","tid":134372,"uid":620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T13:08:25.000Z","msg":"沙灘游到較深位置遇溺<br />\n最後比救生員救起"},{"pid":"5198ff701dbc6fb2884e0821f59f872da1c23339","tid":134372,"uid":11211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T13:46:17.000Z","msg":"爭少少游輸左出唔到世"},{"pid":"48211c9d8aa269512011c338b42340435009207d","tid":134372,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"你老母而家仲危險過你啊 挽你老母"},{"pid":"f7cd484787e6127e3558791a4a3f03b7ff0b7b62","tid":134372,"uid":74002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:24:59.000Z","msg":"玩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98e4d3d1855071a8ea22c321820471872d2b47f","tid":134372,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}